How to use "transition" tools?

	1. Gen the POS list from the corpus of authors by using
		POS_frequency.sh
	2. Gen the Transition corpus
		transition_genCorpus.php
	3. Process your text file with the same treatment that are be doing with both before
		transition_file.php
	4. Use some proper tools to compare them
		transition_matching.php

How to read the transition corpus compilation?
	Columns: 	origin tag
	Line: 		tag read after the origin tag
